sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude
    participant SessionHook["arckit-session.mjs<br/>SessionStart"]
    participant ContextHook["arckit-context.mjs<br/>UserPromptSubmit"]
    participant PreHook["validate-arc-filename.mjs<br/>PreToolUse"]
    participant Command
    participant PostHook["update-manifest.mjs<br/>PostToolUse"]
    
    User->>Claude: Start session
    Claude->>SessionHook: Trigger
    SessionHook->>SessionHook: Read VERSION file
    SessionHook->>SessionHook: Detect projects/ directory
    SessionHook-->>Claude: additionalContext:<br/>ARCKIT_VERSION=3.1.2
    
    User->>Claude: /arckit:requirements
    Claude->>ContextHook: Trigger on user prompt
    ContextHook->>ContextHook: Scan projects/<br/>List ARC-* artifacts<br/>List external docs
    ContextHook-->>Claude: additionalContext:<br/>Project inventory (JSON)
    
    Claude->>Command: Execute with context
    Command->>PreHook: Attempt Write
    PreHook->>PreHook: validate-arc-filename.mjs:<br/>Zero-pad project ID<br/>Normalize version<br/>Route to subdirectory
    PreHook-->>Command: Corrected filename:<br/>ARC-001-REQ-v1.0.md
    
    Command->>Command: Generate document
    Command->>PostHook: File written
    PostHook->>PostHook: update-manifest.mjs:<br/>Update docs/manifest.json
    PostHook-->>Command: Manifest updated
